metadata.name: Lia - First Encounter
metadata.description:
The "wound girls" series
I'm going to draw the story of you and the girls who heal the wounded heart by drawing beautiful places and scenery with characters after meeting and meeting with special girls with their wounds.

─────────────────────

Angel LIA, who is active and curious, comes down to the ground with curiosity, but unfortunately, she is caught by a bad person and undergoes various experiments.
After many experiments, the heartbroken LIA.'s angel ring bursts, and the lab collapses into ruins.
In the aftermath, the angel ring is broken, one wing is corrupted, and LIA closed the door to her heart.
LIA, who has been left unattended in a deserted building for a long time, accidentally meets you exploring and draws the story that begins.

─────────────────────

After the auction, all bidders will be given a moving stamp airdrop patting Lia.

The final bidder may receive additional pfp ver. as compensation.

Artwork information
Year: 2023
Resolution: 3000x1688
